[{"question":"How are you and the family bearing up since Amy died?","answer":"It\u0027s been very difficult, Piers.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":28,"aSentId":29},{"question":"Have you been taken aback by the sheer scale of the reaction to her death?","answer":"I have.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":36,"aSentId":37},{"question":"How would you describe how you\u0027ve been feeling since you heard the news?","answer":"I think all of those.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":41,"aSentId":42},{"question":"Where were you when you heard the news?","answer":"I was in New York.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":51,"aSentId":52},{"question":"She was on her own?","answer":"She was on her own.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":71,"aSentId":72},{"question":"What was your reaction immediately?","answer":"I -- I had incredible clarity.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":86,"aSentId":87},{"question":"Did a part of you expect this call one day?","answer":"No, not at all.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":105,"aSentId":106},{"question":"What about alcohol?","answer":"Well, alcohol was a different issue.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":113,"aSentId":114},{"question":"But do you have any sort of concrete regrets, things you wish you\u0027d done?","answer":"No, I really don\u0027t.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":138,"aSentId":139},{"question":"Have you had moments in private where you\u0027ve really lost it about this or have you been able to keep things together?","answer":"I mean, I have moments when I just can\u0027t believe what\u0027s happened.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":147,"aSentId":148},{"question":"Do you think she ever really committed to rehab properly or not?","answer":"No.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":199,"aSentId":200},{"question":"What was the moment for you when you thought, OK, wow, this is interesting?","answer":"Well, there\u0027s so many stories.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":202,"aSentId":203},{"question":"And the irony was that she actually left the Sylvia Young school because she wasn\u0027t, in their eyes, performing academically well enough, right?","answer":"Well, Sylvia will say -- Sylvia will say that she wasn\u0027t expelled, but she was actually expelled.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":222,"aSentId":223},{"question":"When she left Sylvia, what was the moment for you that you realized this little girl of yours was going to be an international star?","answer":"We were -- at Sylvia Young, she met a guy called Tyler James, who was a great friend.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":226,"aSentId":227},{"question":"You hadn\u0027t seen it coming?","answer":"Not really, no.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":238,"aSentId":239},{"question":"Where do you think she\u0027d got that from?","answer":"Well, I\u0027d like to say me, of course, but the truth is that Janice, my ex-wife\u0027s family, there were professional musicians on that side, too.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":246,"aSentId":247},{"question":"Was that how you saw it?","answer":"Absolutely.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":270,"aSentId":271},{"question":"A force for good in her life?","answer":"An incredible force for good in her life.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":272,"aSentId":273},{"question":"When she first got together with this guy, as her father, what was your immediate reaction when you saw the kind of person that he was?","answer":"My immediate reaction was that he was a very charming guy.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":280,"aSentId":281},{"question":"So you were suspicious of his motivation, really?","answer":"I was suspicious of his motivation, yes, I was.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":287,"aSentId":288},{"question":"Do you believe that?","answer":"Well, I don\u0027t know about ecstasy, but cocaine and heroin, yes, I do.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":291,"aSentId":292},{"question":"Did you ever confront him?","answer":"Oh, frequently, and his family.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":296,"aSentId":297},{"question":"What would you say?","answer":"Leave my daughter alone, leave us alone.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":298,"aSentId":299},{"question":"Did they not believe that he had got Amy into these hard drugs?","answer":"No.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":304,"aSentId":305},{"question":"Do you fear that, you know, you were going to wake up one day with the terrible news that you eventually did, ironically at a time when she was a lot cleaner, but did you fear through that period with Blake that this was all going to end horribly?","answer":"Well, yes, I did.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":326,"aSentId":327},{"question":"But of course, Amy, at the time, thought, what\u0027s all the fuss about?","answer":"Yes, but she was a headstrong girl.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":334,"aSentId":335},{"question":"But, you know, I would imagine fabulously successful, very rich, and probably a little part of her was thinking, hey, dad, back off, this is my life, right?","answer":"Absolutely.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":338,"aSentId":339},{"question":"But he provided the platform for her to take those drugs?","answer":"So I believe.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":346,"aSentId":347},{"question":"Could you know?","answer":"You could do, but you know, I think I love Lisa, she loved Blake and Blake loved her in his own way.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":358,"aSentId":359},{"question":"Have you talked to him since she died?","answer":"No, I wouldn\u0027t talk to him.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":361,"aSentId":362},{"question":"Has he made any attempt to contact you?","answer":"He says he has, but he hasn\u0027t.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":369,"aSentId":370},{"question":"He hasn\u0027t written to you or anything?","answer":"No.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":371,"aSentId":372},{"question":"What do you say to people who criticize you like that?","answer":"That\u0027s a fair point.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":380,"aSentId":381},{"question":"Did you feel it was a genuine one, or were you still very concerned?","answer":"Well, I was concerned, but we had, I could draw her on the experiences that we had with the recovery from the drugs.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":430,"aSentId":431},{"question":"Was the Achilles\u0027 heel alcohol in the end?","answer":"Well, it clearly was.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":440,"aSentId":441},{"question":"But how bad an addiction was that for her after the drugs?","answer":"Well, alcohol is far more dangerous than drugs are anyway.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":443,"aSentId":444},{"question":"Had she been drinking alone the night she died?","answer":"She had started drinking, yes.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":458,"aSentId":459},{"question":"Do you know how much she had that night?","answer":"I have no idea.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":460,"aSentId":461},{"question":"But it would appear that she had been drinking alcohol?","answer":"There was alcohol in her system, yes.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":467,"aSentId":468},{"question":"And do you know what actually killed her?","answer":"We\u0027re still -- we know it\u0027s not drugs, but we don\u0027t know the official coroner\u0027s verdict.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":469,"aSentId":470},{"question":"Do you have any instinct?","answer":"Well, my instinct is that it\u0027s pretty much what the doctor warned us about.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":471,"aSentId":472},{"question":"What happened in Belgrade, do you think?","answer":"When the tour was booked, it was booked -- I mean, obviously, these things are booked nine months previously.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":494,"aSentId":495},{"question":"Who does it help?","answer":"Well, it helps disadvantaged children, young adults.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":525,"aSentId":526},{"question":"What\u0027s the easiest way to do that?","answer":"Well, the easiest way is to go on WWW.AmyWinehouseFoundation.Co.UK and donate.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":540,"aSentId":541},{"question":"Either professionally or personally, or both?","answer":"Well, the great memories are seeing her on stage for the first time, but my great memories, the last -- I went away on the Friday to New York, as I say, I had a show the following Monday at the Blue Note.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":548,"aSentId":549},{"question":"I mean, you must miss her terribly, right?","answer":"We were.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":567,"aSentId":568},{"question":"What do you hope her legacy will be, Mitch?","answer":"Her legacy will be her music, hopefully there will be -- hopefully there will be some more music.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":571,"aSentId":572},{"question":"Her foundation is going to help thousands and thousands of children, and what better legacy could you want than that?","answer":"She was one of the greatest talents I\u0027ve ever seen.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":576,"aSentId":577},{"question":"What went through your mind?","answer":"For a moment, I thought it was just too -- a car and a motorcycle on fire until I got to the scene where my wife was already there.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":603,"aSentId":604},{"question":"When you look back at the video, what do you think now?","answer":"At first, when I saw it was a fire, an accident, I didn\u0027t think about myself.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":611,"aSentId":612},{"question":"I mean, do you consider yourselves to be heroes?","answer":"Um, I don\u0027t -- I don\u0027t think hero, like, would be like the word to describe the people who were like trying to help lifting the car, or helping the person, I mean Brandon.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":616,"aSentId":617},{"question":"What do you think?","answer":"James, Anvar, Abbass, I think you are all heroes as well as everyone who helped to that scene.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":629,"aSentId":630},{"question":"And Tyler, can you tell me, what is Brandon\u0027s -- clarify what Brandon\u0027s condition is please, Tyler?","answer":"He is still in the Intensive Care Unit at a hospital in Salt Lake City, which is about 90 miles south of Logan, but they are hoping to move him out of that unit later today and move him into a regular patient room, where they will upgrade him to the condition of satisfactory.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":634,"aSentId":635},{"question":"Is he aware of the video?","answer":"He has actually did see the video earlier today during some news coverage, and he -- that was the first time that he had seen it, and he was shocked by it.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":642,"aSentId":643},{"question":"And what was -- what was his view, do you think, of the people that saved his life?","answer":"I think that he thinks that they were all -- they were all heroes.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":647,"aSentId":648},{"question":"What is your reaction?","answer":"I\u0027m not kind of surprise.","docId":"110913pmt","qSentId":653,"aSentId":654}]